                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7117" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1114</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8847 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">后共享时代，锋芒初绽 ——中交二航局财务共享演进之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Post-sharing era, the edge is early blooming—— Financial sharing and evolution road of China Communications Construction Company Second Aviation Bureau</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">魏明，李永红，王童瑶，徐亚静</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中交第二航务工程局有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务共享；财务云；数智化转型；数据价值链</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial Sharing；Financial Cloud；Digital Intelligence Transformation； Data Value Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当今，以“大智移云物”为代表的新兴技术正在改变企业和行业的运作规律，也正在构筑财务的新未来。财务云作为连续五年位居“影响中国会计人员的十大信息技术”榜首的新兴技术，为企业完成“后共享时代”数智化转型提供了强有力的技术支撑。作为中国港、中国路、中国桥的重要践行者与贡献者，中交第二航务工程局有限公司也在共享服务的实践和新兴技术的创新应用中积极寻求变革，通过引入建筑行业首个财务云业财协同平台，打破了建筑行业不适合建立共享服务中心的质疑，为完成财务管理由事务型向价值创造型的转型升级搭建平台。本案例以建筑行业建立财务共享服务中心的难点及动因为起点，通过描述财务云实施与运营的过程，引出海量数据清洗、标准化流程再造、业财一体化搭建等重点工作内容，引导学生理解如何应用技术手段为数据赋能、助力企业达到价值再增长，并结合新的时代背景和经济环境做出展望。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Today, the emerging technologies represented by the &quot;great wisdom of moving cloud objects&quot; are changing the operation law of enterprises and industries, and are also building a new future of finance. As an emerging technology that has been ranked at the top of the &quot;top ten information technologies that affect Chinese accounting personnel&quot; for five consecutive years, the financial cloud provides a strong technical support for enterprises to complete the transformation of digital intelligence in the &quot;post-sharing era&quot;. As the port of China, China road, China bridge important practitioners and contributors, in the second navigation engineering bureau co., LTD. Also in sharing service practice and emerging technology innovation application actively seeking change, through the introduction of construction industry first financial cloud industry wealth collaborative platform, broke the construction industry is not suitable for establishing sharing service center, to complete the financial management from the transaction to the transformation and upgrading of value creation platform. This case in the construction industry to establish financial sharing service center difficulties and starting point, through the description of financial cloud implementation and operation process, leads to massive data cleaning, standardized process reengineering, industry integration building key content, guide students to understand how to apply technology to assign data, power enterprises to achieve value growth, and combined with the new era background and economic environment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务共享》、《管理会计理论与实务》、《数据分析与可视化》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资源整合理论；财务共享服务；财务云；业财资税融一体化业；数智化转型；柔性管理理论；数据价值链</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
